  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-PROV-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a provenance chain with an orphan intermediate node that carries no upstream prov:* edges and is not marked as foundational evidence, triggering W-PROV-01.",
